<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> koccaṭapaṉma<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied> tiripuvaṉacakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>cuntarapāṇṭiyatevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="15"><g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattu puliyūrkkoṭṭamāṉa kulottuṅkacoḻavaḷanāṭṭuk kuṉṟattūrnāṭṭu perumāḷ tiruviṭaiyāṭṭam maṇimaṅkalamāṉa <hi rend="grantha">grāmaśi</hi> kāmaṇiccaruppetimaṅkalattu vaṇṭuvarāpati Emperumāḷ koyil Em<supplied reason="omitted">peru</supplied>māṉaṭiyāril Aḻakappe<unclear>ru</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>māḷ māṇikkam Innāyaṉārkku cātta Iṭṭa paṭṭam Oṉṟiṉāl Eḻe Araikkāl māṟi poṉ Irukaḻañce nālu mañcāṭiyum viṟṟu mutalāṉa paṇam <num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> kku Innāyaṉākku tirunāmattukkāṇi <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>ceṉāpatipperuvilai Ākak koṇṭa Ivvūr naṭuvilnārācattuk<unclear>ku</unclear> vaṭakku kiḻai maṅkalavutiyil kiḻciṟakil<note n="362-1">This inscription is left unfinished.</note>
</p>

